I'm an incoming engineering student with a focus on civil and transportation systems. This is where I write up structural and infrastructure failures in detail — what failed, why, and what the failure mode reveals about how the system was supposed to work in the first place — along with analysis of transportation networks and the occasional general note.

Sources for failure case studies are cited inline. Corrections and disagreements are welcome — send them to [your email here].
